  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Union of Constituent Bodies has issued a warning to the President",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The President should step down from the office by the 7th of next month without subjecting the country to further anarchy. If not, the union of thera organizations has warned that they will bring all thera to Colombo and engage in continuous protest.",
        "This has been stated in the letter signed by 11 Theras of the Association of Theras and sent to the President",
        "The President should step down from the office by the 7th of next month without taking the country to a state of anarchy.",
        "If they do not withdraw, we will bring all the Theras in the country to Colombo and carry out a massive protest from the 7th.",
        "We have taken this step because the government has not given a healthy response to the letter sent jointly by the Mahanayaka Theras asking them to act immediately to rectify the problem and anarchic situation facing the country.",
        "Also, it is revealed that the President is deceiving the people after taking an oath to come to power through the votes of the Buddhist people and serve the people in the holy land of Ruvanvelisaya and the holy land where Lord Sri Maha Buddha resides.",
        "Even though 69 lakh majority of the people, including the voters, voted for the President with faith in the President, these people do not have any faith in the President. The people of the country, including the Theras, are not ready to accept Gotabaya Rajapakse as president.",
        "And when the country is witnessing massive destruction, we are making this request because it is the prime duty of the party to consider the situation of 22 million people and take action on their behalf."
      ],
